The Company faces operational risks related to the scarcity of virgin raw materials, such as palm oil, coffee, and various na tural 

extracts. These shortages can increase operational costs for Fine Foods due to competition for supply. As these commodities a re 

subject to stricter regulations, their limited availability and rising costs may negatively impact the continuity of producti on and 

profitability. 

